name: Wallet Blocks Key: Series 1
description: If you swap for/purchase a Wallet Blocks Key: Series 1 OBJKT on Hicetnunc (even on the secondary market), you will receive an additional custom, 1/1 single edition OBJKT that is generated entirely from your Wallet ID.  Once you receive your custom Wallet Blocks OBJKT, you are encouraged to swap the Wallet Blocks Key: Series 1 OBJKT on the secondary market so another collector can generate a custom OBJKT using their Wallet ID.  Created by @JimmyTheGhost.  For more information: www.jimmyweber.com/nft-prjs
